body_html:
Hello,
Same case here (retrained inception v3 model).
I followed everything but still have the same issue like @bazinac had (output leaning always toward single category) when running on android (using the demo example).
Both quantize_graph and eight-bit-calculations(with both quantize_weights and quantize_nodes) have the same issue.
Before quantize - i see speeds at 800ms-1.5sec on each prediction on a s7 edge exynos but great results.
After quantize/eightbit i see 350ms-800ms speeds but predictions are always the same class.
